file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: API Fixture
  description: API fixture description
  license:
    name: Apache2
  contact:
    email: support@example.com
servers:
  - url: https://api.example.com/v1
tags:
  - name: Test
    description: Test tag
paths:
  /tests:
    get:
      summary: Test operation
      description: Test operation description
      operationId: test
      tags:
        - Test
      parameters:
        - name: started_utc
          in: query
          description: Some query param
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: stopped
          in: query
          description: Some query param
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: created
          in: query
          description: Some query param
          schema:
            type: string
            format: date-time
            example: 2020-01-01T12:00:00Z
      responses:
        "204":
          description: Response description
